name: TEENAGE MUTANT NINJA TURTLES CARD HOLDER
description:
This travel card holder is made from a page of a reclaimed Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Annual which has been encased in a sturdy vinyl.

It's extremely durable as the vinyl is doubled with the book page sandwiched inside. Our products are not laminated, we use a special thick vinyl that is pliable and very tactile. It's stitched with a super strong thread so it's tough and sturdy.

It has two clear pockets on the inside made from the same clear vinyl. They're the perfect size for travel cards, rail cards, oyster cards, bank cards, id cards, metro cards, bus tickets, business cards and any other peripheral that is credit card size.

Dimensions: height approx 7cm x width 9.5cm when closed. (2.8" x 3.7")

As each item is handmade there may be differences to the one shown, this means your new card holder will be one of a kind.
